SUMMARY:St. Paddy's Day with Pardon The Interruption LIVE! Featuring (extra) Special Guests Gas Money!
DESCRIPTION:This St. Patrick’s Day\, grab your best (green) dancin’ shoes and come on down to WonderStump!\nPardon the Interruption serves up ska-fueled funk\, rock\, reggae\, soul\, and upbeat jams– turning the night into a full-body celebration. High spirits\, happy feet\, and serious bounce guaranteed! \nGas Money will hit the stage to open up and get the blood pumpin’\, the funk-rock vibes groovin’\, and the energy sky high! \nWonderStump is an intentionally designed space for movement and flow. Enjoy the full-room energy without the crush of an overpacked venue! Creative attire encouraged\, immersive surprises in store\, light snacks and bevvies available for purchase. \nDoors at 6:30\, music at 7– with special guests opening ✨ \n$20 presale or hit us with $25 at the door 😎 \nall ages\nnonalcoholic drinks & craft mocktails available!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/st-paddys-day-with-pardon-the-interruption-live-featuring-extra-special-guests/
LOCATION:WonderStump!\, 301 Petaluma Blvd. N. Suite B\, Petaluma\, CA\, 94952\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Pardon-the-interruption-band-2s.jpg
END:VEVENT
