SUMMARY:The Gypsy Trio at Rio Nido Roadhouse
DESCRIPTION:Take a midweek break with great tunes\, delicious food\, and refreshing drinks at Unwind Wednesday — our weekly live music series! \nWhat to Expect: • Live music from local and regional artists • Special food & drink offerings — enjoy great meal deals and featured beverages • Relaxed redwood atmosphere — perfect for unwinding mid-week \nGypsy Trio delivers a vibrant\, rhythm-driven blend of acoustic world music\, fiery gypsy jazz\, Latin grooves\, and soulful reinterpretations of classic favorites. With rich instrumentation and tight musical chemistry\, the trio creates an immersive live experience that feels both intimate and electrifying. \nRooted in the traditions of Django Reinhardt-inspired gypsy jazz and global acoustic sounds\, Gypsy Trio weaves together expressive guitar work\, melodic leads\, dynamic percussion\, and warm harmonies. Their performances move effortlessly between upbeat\, danceable rhythms and sultry\, romantic ballads — creating a soundscape that transports listeners from European cafés to Spanish courtyards and beyond. \nKnown for their engaging stage presence and musical finesse\, Gypsy Trio brings both artistry and joy to every performance.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/the-gypsy-trio-at-rio-nido-roadhouse/
LOCATION:Rio Nido Roadhouse\, 14540 Canyon 2 Road\, Rio Nido\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.5205;-122.979
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Rio Nido Roadhouse 14540 Canyon 2 Road Rio Nido CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=14540 Canyon 2 Road:geo:-122.979,38.5205
END:VEVENT
