SUMMARY:The Joe Campbell Quartet at The Big Easy
DESCRIPTION:Drummer / composer Joe Campbell debuts his quartet to showcase an evening of jazz music from a tight-knit group of frequent collaborators who have worked together for years. The band will be playing new original music along with some familiar classics. Featuring Patrick Gallagher on keys\, and brothers Daniel and Cam Urquhart on guitar and bass respectively.
